==English==

===Etymology===
Possible literal translation from Chinese

===Phrase===
'''[[long]] [[time]] [[no]] [[see]]'''
#{{idiom}} I haven't seen you in too long.
#:''Dave!  '''Long time no see'''!  How has Boston been treating you?''

====Translations====
*Czech: [[dlouho jsme se neviděli]]
